{"tid":1478951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世文］連登已經彌漫一種自殺風氣，再落去肯定會出事","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T12:35:45.000Z","uid":35699,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a768be2897a655cccf4ada154a464377345717f3","tid":1478951,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"長話短說，就係818有人主張和理非會合，曲線煽動連登仔唔帶裝備裸跑式參加集會。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我想講：我屌晒你哋老母！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家狗狗已經會亂射催淚性神經毒氣，我知你哋威可以用普通口罩做滅火隊，但係呢啲毒素會永遠積存你哋體內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，對健康有急性同慢性影響，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以一定要full gear</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而blackbloc 可以增加辨認難度，除非你哋唔想保護手足啦，如果唔係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔該有咁黑著咁黑！！</span></span>，做完運動記得換裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外就係用過食煙嘅面罩記得棄置！物資雖然珍貴，但個人認為無必要帶埋啲受污染嘅裝備返屋企，當然大家可以命運自決，只能夠講污染咗嘅嘢一定要掉！！ 食過煙嘅衫褲都唔好洗！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k72LU36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk72LU36.jpg&h=c3322339&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a66500e85a328687acb25d3d3d4f937e0668cb5c","tid":1478951,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0560c8154eb9d8b6e8a1c5bfd0f9d4843cadf285","tid":1478951,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:04:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd813f27ac2f01d5d370933d8f49b81db38b9d13","tid":1478951,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccb4fed930394a74ea25a58333133146d05e6b18","tid":1478951,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0560c8154eb9d8b6e8a1c5b